{"tid":669492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友好鍾意聞我格肋底","createTime":"2018-05-18T13:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T16:05:56.000Z","uid":50732,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"79a08a15e1240677f6edf223276fa11627c013eb","tid":669492,"uid":50732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"呢排夏天好易出汗<br />\n佢成日行行下街一個手插入我格肋底<br />\n之後拎去聞 <br />\n有時行行下街又係咁渣我個波 又係咁我搞粒lin<br />\n得閒又摸下我屎忽<br />\n有日係屋企沖涼 <br />\n沖完涼出黎見到佢拎我條底褲放係塊面係咁索<br />\n訓訓下又係爬去聞我隻腳 話好臭 <br />\n仲話想聞我全身都係汗果陣<br />\n上次柯完屎 佢又即刻沖入去聞 話好正<br />\n有時真係懷疑佢前世係咪變態啊叔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢想像兩年同佢一齊住會發生咩事<br />\n有無人女朋友都係咁 定我果個特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dcf6a9e88bb2896f3cbd3afb082e69242cc5b2","tid":669492,"uid":154131,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcebf9dd79d5228a160d84d7ef1d885c34e89820","tid":669492,"uid":148056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"3c49f9b76d50b4ff0b7c83ae17c5d8d3544f355b","tid":669492,"uid":168671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"試下對住佢塊面放屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de31e203644294d593b4e02ddb2d771f562b3235","tid":669492,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3d89ed172412c3eb05c6fa7e930da1991b58d2","tid":669492,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"你聞返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d804a993a359630bac2cb5b0a3ca549c369403e","tid":669492,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited